data.description: Welcome to this well laid out sprawling Ranch. With so much more space than it looks you'll be excited to call this home. Move in ready and updates throughout you'll love the Beautiful Hardwood floors, updated vinyl windows, and warming brick gas fireplace. The open living/dining combination offers lots of Natural Light throughout the home. The galley style Kitchen with all appliances staying, plent of cupboard space and also offers a deep pantry and Sliding glass doors for easy access to your Large wooden deck. A spacious Master bedroom with Built in desk and two additional bedrooms with generously sized closets round out the bedrooms on the main floor. A Remodeled Full bathroom with title Shower and modern vanity will give you years of comfort and ease of use. A very large Family room complete with its own door for entry and access for the garage give you ample space to entertain or use as a nice area of your choosing. The lower level gives you even more room for potential for your imagination to run wild. Complete with a Bonus room, A nicely updated full bathroom, A very large rec room, and Large laundry/storage area this area is its own escape. The property sits on a well-maintained and peaceful street. A large Fenced in back yard gives you ample amounts of private space. A large wood deck will have you enjoying cook outs and entertaining in no time. A 1.5 car garage for additional storage and  with a pull through rear garage door makes Mowing and moving items in and out a breeze. With so much to offer, schedule your appointment today before it's too late.
